"Zĩ-kãnga, d tõe n maana sũ-noog ne b sẽn sak yʋʋm 2020 soabã, sẽn tũ ne tʋʋm noor ning b sẽn boond tɩ ""milenyʋm Sal̄ẽns Korporasẽo"" a vuk a yiib n soabã sẽn gomd Burkĩna Faso kʋra wã yellã."
